OL,3,CInmates return to HMP Dartmoor amid
OL,4,C'new regime' to remove radon gas
OL,6,FInmates who were transferred from a
OL,7,Fprison after high levels of
OL,8,Fradioactive gas were detected are
OL,9,Fbeing returned.
OL,11,FHundreds of prisoners were moved from
OL,12,FHMP Dartmoor, in Devon, after the
OL,13,FHealth and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,14,Flaunched an investigation into radon
OL,15,Fexposures at the site in December 2023.
OL,17,FIt is understood that 30 prisoners are
OL,18,Fdue to be returning to the site each
OL,19,Fweek, amid of "new regime of purging
OL,20,Fradon gas" from affected areas.
