OL,3,CInmates return to HMP Dartmoor amid
OL,4,C'new regime' to remove radon gas
OL,6,FA Prison Service spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Prisoners will be gradually returned
OL,8,Fto HMP Dartmoor following
OL,9,Fconversations with the Health and
OL,10,FSafety Executive and we have ongoing
OL,11,Fmitigations in place to limit radon
OL,12,Fexposure."
OL,14,F"We continue to engage closely with
OL,15,Fthe Health and Safety Executive and we
OL,16,Fwill regulalry review the situation,"
OL,17,Fthey added.
