OL,3,CInmates return to HMP Dartmoor amid
OL,4,C'new regime' to remove radon gas
OL,6,FIt is understood the Ministry of
OL,7,FJustice (MoJ) has put "appropriate
OL,8,Fmitigations" in place which have been
OL,9,Fagreed with the Health and Safety
OL,10,FExecutive (HSE).
OL,12,FThe MoJ said HMP Dartmoor will be
OL,13,Fimplementing a "new regime" of purging
OL,14,Fgas in the atmopshere by opening
OL,15,Fwindows, doors and roof vents three
OL,16,Ftimes a day.
OL,18,FThese new ventilation measures will
OL,19,Fwork alongside a regime of "live
OL,20,Ftesting" radon levels in several
OL,21,Fcells, the MoJ said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
