OL,3,CInmates return to HMP Dartmoor amid
OL,4,C'new regime' to remove radon gas
OL,6,FIt added prisoner transfers into HMP
OL,7,FDartmoor recommenced on 1 July 2024.
OL,9,FRadon, an odourless and colourless
OL,10,Fgas, is produced by decaying
OL,11,Fradioactive materials in rocks and
OL,12,Fsoils, and is responsible for around
OL,13,F1,000 lung cancer deaths a year.
OL,15,FIt is thought to occur more often in
OL,16,Fareas with high concentrations of
OL,17,Fgranite, such as Dartmoor.
OL,19,FAn HSE Executive confirmed that an
OL,20,Finvestigation into radon exposures at
OL,21,Fthe Category C prison is ongoing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
