OL,3,CInmates return to HMP Dartmoor amid
OL,4,C'new regime' to remove radon gas
OL,6,F"We have written to His Majesty's
OL,7,FPrison and Probation Service (HMPPS)
OL,8,Finforming them of legal requirements
OL,9,Frelating to radon exposures. The legal
OL,10,Fduty to keep prisoners and staff safe
OL,11,Frests with HMPPS," an HSE spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"However, our investigation is ongoing
OL,15,Fand we cannot comment further at this
OL,16,Ftime."
